New De lhi, the 4th Novem ber, 1969.
13th Kartika, 1391.
The undersigned is directed to state that with
effect from the forenoon of Novem ber 4, 1969,
(i) Shri Bali Ram Bhagat relinquished the office
of Minister of Foreign Trade and Supply and
assumed the office of Minister of Foreign
Trade; and
(li) Shri R.X. Khadilkar assumed the office of
Minister of State in-charge of the Ministry
of Supply.
(R.N. Kalia)
for Cabinet Secretary.

All Members of the Council of Ministers.

the Joint Secretary to the Prime Minister/the Private Secretary

the Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
(RN. Kalia
